"unprivileged users to see other running processes in execution by other "
"groups (GID) preventing information leakage."
msgstr ""

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:806
msgid ""
"`hide_jail` - Hide processes running in jails to prevent the unprivileged "
